MNUMBER 265
NAME drone
ADJECTIVE 45
*DESCRIPTION_START
The Vith drone is smaller than the females. He is colored with a black head and limbs on a yellow body, although he also displays limited blending ability. The drone only stands about three feet tall, but his small size makes him lightning quick. His wings are hideously deformed, but his huge stinger is not.
*DESCRIPTION_END
