MNUMBER 266
UNIQUE
NAME Hhrixlix
*DESCRIPTION_START
You gaze onto the bloated monstrosity known as Hhrixlix. Hhrixlix is the queen of the Vith. She is not much taller than four feet tall. The Vith queen's markings are yellow on black instead of the reverse. She has a grossly distended thorax, which make you wonder how she gets around. Her rainbow colored compound eyes radiate magical power. Hhrixlix has huge mandibles which drip with some sort of fluid.
*DESCRIPTION_END
