MNUMBER 222
NAME Moiya
;PART ?
*DESCRIPTION_START
You see Moiya, a old female gurkan.
She is tall, lightweight and frail.
She has black eyes, greenish black skin that glistens, and a red crest
that terminates behind her neck. Her webbed hands bear no adornment.
She is wearing a simple bone talisman on a fibrous cord.
*DESCRIPTION_END
