MNUMBER 223
NAME Instadtoo
*DESCRIPTION_START
You see Instadtoo, an incredibly old female gurkan.
She is tall, emaciated and feeble.
Her greenish black skin has dried to a wrinkly crust. Her once red crest
is now a dull brown and droops a bit. Her eyes are closed, and she holds
her webbed hands clasped in her lap.
She is wearing a light kelp thread cape.
*DESCRIPTION_END
