Long, black tentacles extrude from the back of this lurching humanoid
figure, almost as if some intelligence had crawled inside a human and
was now using the body to live in. The creature's white skin is covered
with running scabs and sores, and crimson red lights glow evilly in the
creature's eye sockets. A pulsating grey horn grows from the center of
the forhead, and you can see the horn begin to hum with power as the
creature looks at you. The most horrifying aspect of the creature are
the small, clear gems that are set into its body. Within the gems can
be seen the imprisoned souls of the creature's previous victims!
*DESCRIPTION_END
