Tufts of feathers still cling to the bony skeleton of this enormous parrot.
Its razor sharp beak has split down the center, forming two deadly-looking
fangs. Eyeless, it still somehow manages to find its prey, clawing and biting
with a furious frenzy.
*DESCRIPTION_END
