You see Thorgon Mightythew, a young male highlander.
He is short, heavy and incredibly muscular.
He has blue eyes, tan skin and pony-tailed black hair.
He is wearing some charcoal gray crystal mail with highly articulated arm and
shoulder joints to allow weaponsmithing, a glowing amulet, some black leather
boots with bits of hammered metal affixed in strategic locations and a dented
gray crystal helm with a hammer buried in the bloody dent on top.
He appears to be healthy.
He has a singed back.
*description_end
