*DESCRIPTION_START
Standing before you, you see a large demon which appears in many ways to
be similar to a toad. Its body is rotund and bloated. Its stumpy hind
legs can hardly propel its mass at all. The laash's forlimbs are huge,
bear enormous muscles and terminate in huge filthy claws. You can
occasionally see the laash's tongue, which is long, sticky and barbed.
It gazes at you with yellow, slitted eyes.
*DESCRIPTION_END
