MNUMBER 296
NAME skurspyr
*DESCRIPTION_START
You sense the dreaded skurspyr before you actually see it. It takes all
of your perception to see it and all of your willpower to tear your gaze
away. The demon is a small, mostly phased humanoid. You can make out
two arms, legs and hands. One of the hands clutches a slender knife. The
skurspyr's tiny head and long neck only seem to serve as a home for a
odd suction cup. Its one huge eye gazes at you from the center of its
chest.
*DESCRIPTION_END
