MNUMBER 298
NAME diagru
*DESCRIPTION_START
Your gaze falls upon a diagru, or bone lord. This horrific demon is said
to only be able to be spawned in the runed cauldron of Krajj, when it is
filled with the bones of innocents. The diagru stands a hulking nine
feet high. It is armored from top to bottom with plates of solid bone.
Its face is that of an innocent babe, except that the babe's face is
made of bone and leers at you hungrily. In its hands is a wicked-looking
razor scythe.
