*DESCRIPTION_START
A thin cloud of misty ice particles hovers around the black obsidian form
of the Darakoth. Bred in the Ice Pits of Daraal these fearsome warriors are
the fighters of the their Race. They are tall and heavy humanoid looking
figures with two, large wings, that appear to be made of black ice,
extending nearly five feet from their backs. Their oval, slick faces contain
two, pulsating slits where the nose should be, and a gaping hole, ringed
with black death for a mouth. Two thin openings are set where the eyes
should be, small yellow pinpricks glowing eerily from within the openings.
Sharp talons steadily grip a sword made from hardened black ice...
*DESCRIPTION_END
