; TEXC A captain orders his group
; TEXB A group moves in under the command of a demon captain.
;
; Dark Guardian
MNUMBER 337
NAME guardian
ADJECTIVE 81
HUMAN
BODY 150
ATTACK1 100
DEFENSE 120
STRATEGY 510
IMMUNITY 0 0
IMMUNITY 5 0
IMMUNITY 7 0
IMMUNITY 8 2
RACE 22
WEAPON 18 197 100
WEAPONPLUS 10
ARMOR 40
MAGICWEAPON 2
FATIGUE 25 10
RESIST 75
PSIRESIST 90
SPEED 3
ALIGNMENT -10
*DESCRIPTION_START
The dark guardian is composed of swirling black mists in a vaguely humanoid
form. Its exact origins are unknown, but its appearance gives visions of the
lightless domains.
*DESCRIPTION_END
DISCORPORATE
;
MNUMBER 312
NAME gargoyle
ADJECTIVE 6
HUMAN
PART 15
PART 16
PART 17
BODY 300
ATTACK1 220
DEFENSE 220
MAGICWEAPON 2
STRATEGY 501
WEAPON 279 -1 10
POISON 50 15
RESIST 100
PSIRESIST 100
RACE 21
DISCORPORATE
*DESCRIPTION_START
Much larger than its cousins, the greater gargoyle is an imposing sight.
Curving talons drip with a foul-smelling ichor from its hands and feet, and
its huge membranous wings furiously beat the air.
*DESCRIPTION_END
TEXD explodes in a cloud of noxious fumes.
TEXM A gargoyle flies
;
MNUMBER 130
NAME warrior
ADJECTIVE 74
ATTACK1 200
BODY 250
RESIST 200
PSIRESIST 200
EXTRABODY 500
DEFENSE 502
armor 30
DISCORPORATE
HUMAN
IMMUNITY 6 0
IMMUNITY 7 0
STRATEGY 501
GENDER 1
TEXD falls to the ground and gasps once before turning to mist and dispersing.
TEXM A spectral warrior strides
WEAPON 18 -1 100
WEAPONPLUS 2
SCRIPTMACRO 57
;
MACRO 57
IFPREVERB LOOK -1
  IFVAR ALIGN < -10
    ECHO PLAYER You are unable to look upon the creature without feeling ill. You feel a
    ECHO PLAYER burning in your eyes, and as you turn away, everything becomes dizzy.
    IFVAR INTNUM3 ! 1
      DAMAGEPLR BODYONLY 70 You clutch your stomach and fall to the ground.
      ECHO OTHERS %N clutches %h stomach and falls to the ground!
      POSITION LAY
    ENDIF
  ELSE
    IFVAR ALIGN < 10
      ECHO PLAYER You can make out an outline of a female figure, but the harder you try to make
      ECHO PLAYER out distinct features, the more the image seems to fade away.
    ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER Before you stands a strangely beautiful woman with pale blue skin and ivory
      ECHO PLAYER hair. Her pained expression is visible through the white haze that surrounds
      ECHO PLAYER her.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB KISS -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR ALIGN < 0
    ECHO PLAYER %A glares at you and steps away.
    ECHO OTHERS As %n tries to kiss a spectral warrior, she glares at %i and steps away.
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER You kiss a spectral warrior upon the cheek.
    ECHO OTHERS %N kisses a spectral warrior upon the cheek.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
;

